\'fc, bilindi\'f0i \'fczere, T\'fcrkiye'nin G\'fcneydo\'f0u b\'f6lgesinde 15 y\'fdld\'fdr kan d\'f6ken, binlerce polis ve askerimizi \'feehit eden b\'f6l\'fcc\'fc ter\'f6r \'f6rg\'fct\'fc, a\'e7\'fdk\'e7a kom\'fcnist ideolojiye sahip bir \'f6rg\'fctt\'fc
