\par }\pard \qj \fi567\li0\ri0\sl-340\slmult0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f101\fs22\insrsid6554430 Darwin'in teorisini ge\'e7ersiz k\'fdlan ikinci b\'fcy\'fck nokta, teorinin "evrim mekanizmalar\'fd" olarak \'f6ne s\'fcrd\'fc\'f0\'fc
